DESCRIPTION:You are cordially invited to attend our Documentary Premiere.\n
 On Saturday October 29\, 2022\, we are turning Mike's Dance Barn into a mov
 ie theater for the first showing of our film\, Houston's History of C&W Dan
 ce.\n\n\n5:00 PM Doors open\nA Tex Mex buffet will be provided by Mikes Dan
 ce Barn.\nAnd browse our Preserve the past-Ignite the Future Hall of Fame g
 allery\n6:00 First showing of the film\n7:00 PM  Jim Hayden and the Country
  Playboys’ 7 piece band playing fabulous dance music and everyone’s country
  favorites…\nWe will be celebrating Mickey Gilley for his influence on the 
 country craze of the 1980's. And in honor of Urban Cowboy\, there will be a
  Bud and Sissy look alike contest - and a surprise photo booth with props- 
 you don’t wanna miss! \nGames and dance lessons too.\n\nA full night of fun
 !\n\nCall/Text to reserve your tickets today $35 per person. Includes Tex M
 ex buffet\, film\, live music\, and games. Plus the fun photo booth. \nAnd 
 the Preserve the Past-Ignite the Future Hall of Fame Gallery\n\n812 322-160
 3\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/3464793073801612/
LAST-MODIFIED:20221012T211154Z
LOCATION:Mike's Music & Dance Barn
SEQUENCE:1989320
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Film Premiere/Gilley's comes to Indiana
TRANSP:OPAQUE
