 le month collaborating with local artists to create pieces for this art sho
 w: InterACTION!\n\nInterACTION revolves around two central themes: interact
 ion and movement. Students work with Bloomington artists like Joel Washingt
 on and Sarah Wolfe to create unique displays that engage both their creativ
 ity and viewers.\n\nFREE ADMISSION - Part of the First Friday Gallery Walk\
 nAppetizers and refreshments will be served throughout the event.\n\nSelect
  works will be displayed in Fountain Square Mall through May.\n\nFollow @ha
 rmonyschoolbloomington on social media for updates!\n\nContact: Olivia Thro
 ckmartin\nEmail: olivia@harmonyschool.org\nPhone: 812-334-8388
