  Humanity’s 2025 Women+ Build. 🏗️🧩</p><p>📝 <strong>What to Expect:</stro
 ng></p><ul><li><p>Doors open at <strong>5:30 PM</strong>\; trivia begins at
  <strong>6:00 PM</strong> sharp</p></li><li><p>Play as a team (4–6 people r
 ecommended)</p></li><li><p>Lighthearted\, inclusive questions and prizes fo
 r top teams!</p></li></ul><p>💵 <strong>Donation:</strong></p><ul><li><p>$2
 0 per player<br><a>Make your donation here</a><br>(Add <em>“Trivia Night”</
 em> in the comment field when donating)</p></li></ul><p>🍎 <strong>Perks:</
 strong></p><ul><li><p>Snacks and drinks (alcoholic and non-alcoholic) avail
 able for purchase</p></li><li><p>All ages welcome — bring the whole family!
 </p></li></ul><p>📧 Contact: <a>boswell@monroecountyhabitat.org</a><br>🛠️ 
 100% of proceeds go toward building affordable housing in Monroe County!</p
 >
