 tival Benefiting PALS!</p><p>Join us for a spooky and heartwarming evening 
 on <strong>Friday\, October 25th from 5–8 PM</strong> at:</p><p>📍 <strong>
 7644 W Elwren Rd.\, Bloomington\, IN 47403</strong></p><p>This family-frien
 dly event supports People &amp\; Animal Learning Services (PALS) and featur
 es:</p><p>✨ Trick-or-treating on the sensory trail<br>🎶 Live music &amp\; 
