 p\; festive fun for all ages</p><p>🎟️ <strong>Admission &amp\; Tickets</st
 rong><br>➡️ <em>Pre-register online through Oct 23 at 11:59 PM:</em></p><ul
 ><li><p>$7 per person (under 3 free)</p></li><li><p>Discounted activity tic
 kets available</p></li></ul><p>➡️ <em>At the door (Oct 25):</em></p><ul><li
 ><p>$10 per person (under 3 free)</p></li><li><p>Activity tickets: $1 each<
 /p></li></ul><p>🔗 Register &amp\; get tickets: <a href="https://palstherap
 y.org/halloween-with-the-horses/">https://palstherapy.org/halloween-with-th
 e-horses/</a></p><p></p><p>⚠️ <em>Note:</em> Admission tickets are required
  to attend. Activity tickets must be purchased separately. All tickets are 
