DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us for the Holiday Gift Fair at Redbud Books! This fund
 raiser features a silent auction\, where amazing gifts\, goods and services
  will be available\, including:<br></p><ul><li>Handmade pottery by local ce
 ramicists</li><li>Custom Tattoo by Jason Profant of Time and Tide Tattoo</l
 i><li>Custom cake by Goopy Goose Baking</li><li>Tickets to local theatrical
  productions</li><li>Gift cards to Office Clothier\, Bloomington Fine Arts 
 Supply\, and other local shops</li><li>HVAC services\, Event Planning\, Ast
 rology Reading\, and other professional services</li></ul><p></p><p>Redbud 
 Books serves the Bloomington community through free weekly events and progr
 amming\, open to the general public. This includes arts programming\, free 
 educational talks and classes\, programs for youth and families\, and progr
 ams with an environmental sustainability focus\, film screenings on topics 
 of local and political relevance\, among others.<br></p>
