DESCRIPTION:Do you have an old telescope\, camera\, or even a set of binocu
 lars? You can use any of these to view the solar eclipse! Join us at Bloomi
 nglabs for our workshop where we will help you make a custom filter to fit 
 your optical device. We'll provide the eye-safe solar film and other materi
 als. You'll also receive tips for safely watching and photographing the ecl
 ipse\, and other fun related science information. This all-ages workshop is
  perfect for everyone interested in the solar eclipse. Please pre-register 
 at http://www.bloominglabs.org. Seats are limited\, so sign up soon!
LAST-MODIFIED:20240313T123115Z
LOCATION:Bloominglabs\, 1840 S Walnut St Suite #200\, Bloomington\, IN 4740
 1\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Solar Eclipse Lens Filter Making Workshop
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
