DESCRIPTION:This will be our 40th Annual Community Book Fair. We will fill 
 two buildings with over 100\,000 books\, DVDs\, CDs\, LPs\, games\, puzzles
  and other items at affordable prices to support the food bank's work. Ther
 e will be a large selection of children's books and collectible "Better Boo
 ks\," which will also include a selection of vintage vinyl LPs. If you wish
  to donate used books CDs\, DVDs\, records\, games and puzzles at the Hoosi
 er Hills Food Bank\, do so between Monday to Friday from 9am to 5pm (2333 W
 . Industrial Park Dr). We won't accept donations of the categories above th
 e entire month of October this year\, that being from the 1st to 31st. For 
 more information regarding this please call (812) 334-8374 or email Ryan at
  volunteer@hhfoodbank.org.
