DESCRIPTION:<p>✨ <strong>Kick off the 32nd Annual Lotus World Music &amp\; 
 Arts Festival</strong> with a vibrant evening of global rhythms\, street fe
 stivities\, and immersive art experiences throughout Bloomington’s beautifu
 l downtown. Day 1 sets the tone for a magical weekend with:</p><ul><li><p><
 strong>🌍 International music performances</strong> across multiple stages<
 /p></li><li><p><strong>🎨 Illuminated art installations</strong> and live s
 treet murals</p></li><li><p><strong>💃 Dance tents</strong> and interactive
  rhythm workshops</p></li><li><p><strong>🛍️ Artisan village</strong> with 
 handmade crafts and global goods</p></li><li><p><strong>🍴 Food vendors</st
 rong> offering international and local cuisine</p></li></ul><p>💬 <em>"A ka
 leidoscope of sound\, culture\, and connection" – Day 1 is your invitation 
 to step into the world.</em></p><p>📌 <strong>Tip:</strong> Arrive early to
  explore venue maps\, grab dinner downtown\, and secure a good spot for hea
 dline shows.</p><p>🔗 Full schedule and updates at <a href="https://lotusfe
 st.org">lotusfest.org</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250609T174555Z
LOCATION:Downtown Bloomington\, 302 S College Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47403\
 , USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Lotus World Music & Arts Festival
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
