DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>What to Expect:</strong><br>Join the City of Bloomin
 gton and Milestone Contractors for the grand opening celebration of Hopewel
 l Commons\, the city’s newest park and public space.<br>Enjoy an afternoon 
 filled with:</p><ul><li><p>🎶 Live music performances</p></li><li><p>🎤 Rem
 arks from special guest speakers (starting at 4:15 PM)</p></li><li><p>🚚 Lo
 cal food trucks offering a variety of tasty options</p></li><li><p>🎯 Fun g
 ames and activities for all ages</p></li><li><p>🧃 Community gathering and 
 celebration in a beautifully revitalized green space</p></li></ul><p><stron
 g>Parking &amp\; Transportation:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Parking Loc
 ation:</strong> Monroe Convention Center\, 302 S. College Ave.</p></li><li>
 <p><strong>Distance to Event:</strong> ~0.26 mile walk south along the B-Li
 ne Trail</p></li><li><p><strong>Accessibility:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Elect
 ric golf cart shuttle available between parking and park</p></li><li><p>Lim
 ited accessible parking on W. University St. east of Rogers St. for vehicle
 s with disabled permits</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Visitors are encouraged to
  walk\, bike\, skate\, or use other non-motorized transportation</p></li><l
 i><p><strong>Bike Parking:</strong> Available along the B-Line Trail and at
  the west end of the park</p></li></ul><p><strong>Facilities &amp\; Sponsor
 ship:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Temporary restrooms will be available onsite</
 p></li><li><p>Entertainment proudly sponsored by Milestone Contractors</p><
 /li><li><p>Hosted by the City of Bloomington Parks and Recreation Departmen
 t</p></li></ul><p><strong>More Info:</strong> <a href="https://bloomington.
 in.gov/parks">https://bloomington.in.gov/parks</a></p>
