DESCRIPTION:Join the gifted local singer-songwriter in his first theatre sh
 owcase.<br><p>Sometimes the finest talent hides in plain sight. Hoosier nat
 ive Jeff Day has been a fixture of the local music scene since his teenage 
 years in the early 90s. He’s the type of artist that “Piano Man” Billy Joel
  was singing about when he quipped “Man\, what are you doing here?” Over de
 cades of performances\, ranging from the smallest intimate gatherings to fu
 ll concert venues\, he has perfected a unique personal style featuring powe
 rful vocals accompanied by his own intricate fingerstyle acoustic guitar ar
 rangements. On the heels of his newly released album “Manifest\,” the time 
 has come for Jeff’s many fans to see his talent showcased in a proper theat
 re setting. Come spend An Evening with Jeff Day!</p><u></u><a href="https:/
 /buskirkchumley.org/event/an_evening_with_jeff_day/">https://buskirkchumley
 .org/event/an_evening_with_jeff_day/</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230125T131651Z
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater\, 114 E Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47
 408\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:An Evening with Jeff Day
TRANSP:OPAQUE
