DESCRIPTION:\nThe City of Bloomington will be hosting the fourth annual Ear
 th Day event at Switchyard Park on Saturday\, April 18\, 2026 from 12:00-3:
 30 p.m.\n\nThe event is FREE and open to the public\, and will feature live
  music from Busman's Holiday and Peyton Womock\, food and drinks\, local ve
 ndors\, tree giveaways\, and more. \n\nThis year's event is hosted as a joi
 nt effort between the Department of Economic and Sustainable Development an
 d the Parks and Recreation Department. Registration is not required. \n\nMo
 re details will be added as we get closer to the event!\n\nFor more informa
 tion visit:\nbloomington.in.gov/sustainability/earthday\n\n\nSPECIAL NOTE: 
 Exhibitor registration for this event is offered ONLY through official staf
 f at the City of Bloomington Department of Economic and Sustainable Develop
 ment. If you see an offer to be an exhibitor at this event through the even
 t discussion\, it should be considered a SCAM.\n\n\nhttps://www.facebook.co
 m/events/870093179531742/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T130000Z
LOCATION:Switchyard Park - City of Bloomington\, IN
SEQUENCE:3354678
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:4th Annual Earth Day Event
TRANSP:OPAQUE
