DESCRIPTION:Innovation Week is a city-wide celebration of innovation\, crea
 tivity\, and collaboration. Hosted by The Mill\, each day highlights a loca
 l innovation cluster:\n\nNov 4 – HealthTech: Advancing care through science
  & collaboration\nNov 5 – GovTech: Tech for communities & security\nNov 6 –
  Artificial Intelligence: How AI reshapes life & industry\nNov 7 – Creative
  Arts & Community: Makers\, artists & the big Block Party at 5 PM\n\nAll ev
 ents are free & open to the public.\nMore info & free tickets: https://dime
 nsionmill.org/innovation-week
