 //www.youtube.com/watch?v=KzsRwiJcGNY</a></p><p>• <strong>WFIU: Remembering
  Janis Stockhouse</strong><br>🎙️ <em>Just You and Me</em> program hosted b
 y David Brent Johnson<br>Contributors: Lissa May\, Rachel Caswell\, Natalie
  Boeyink\, Sara Caswell\, and Thomas Wilson<br>Part 1: <a href="https://www
 .google.com/url?q=https://indianapublicmedia.org/nightlights/remembering-ja
 nis-stockhouse.php&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVa
 w2Y94kSTW9p7wfxpPkdNTGx" target="_blank">https://indianapublicmedia.org/nig
 htlights/remembering-janis-stockhouse.php</a><br>Part 2: <a href="https://w
 ww.google.com/url?q=https://indianapublicmedia.org/nightlights/remembering-
 janis-stockhouse-part-2.php&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;
 usg=AOvVaw1GJ-QEyIle3ML5fb4e_VXO" target="_blank">https://indianapublicmedi
 a.org/nightlights/remembering-janis-stockhouse-part-2.php</a></p><p>• <stro
 ng>Herald-Times Article</strong><br>📰 <em>Janis Stockhouse\, legendary mus
 ic director\, mentor\, dies at 69</em><br><a href="https://www.google.com/u
 rl?q=https://www.heraldtimesonline.com/story/news/local/2024/12/28/janis-st
 ockhouse-bloomington-band-director-educator-dies-at-69/77267725007/&amp\;sa
 =D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0yl2acuX1XiLZgvaXwRpwy" t
