CREATED:20230316T141043Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>10th Annual Spring Swing Dance to be held at Bloomington 
 North High School</b></p><p>The Bloomington High School North Jazz Bands wi
 ll present the 10th Annual Swing Dance on Friday\, March 31st at 7:00 p.m. 
 with a special guest appearance by singer and BHSN alum\, Sadie Johnson. Th
 e event will be held in the BHSN cafe and will include complimentary swing 
 dance lessons provided by the IU Swing Dance Club\, followed by open dancin
 g. Live big band music will be provided by all four BHSN jazz bands and com
 bos under the direction of Janis Stockhouse &amp\; Thomas Wilson. Refreshme
 nts will be available for sale in the form of club mocktails. 1920s – 1940s
  dress is encouraged and will be judged during our costume contest. A dance
  partner is not required. </p><p>Admission is $10.00 for 18 and under/senio
 rs\; $20.00 for adults\; $50 family maximum. Tickets are available at the d
 oor and online. Cash and credit cards are accepted. All proceeds for the ev
 ening will support the BHSN Band program. </p><p>Visit <a href="http://www.
 bhsnbands.com/">www.bhsnbands.com</a> for more details.</p><p><a href="http
 s://ticketscandy.com/e/10th-anniversary-bhsn-swing-dance-1470">https://tick
 etscandy.com/e/10th-anniversary-bhsn-swing-dance-1470</a></p><p><b>About BH
 SN Jazz Bands<br></b>Bloomington High School North has a stellar jazz progr
 am. It offers four jazz band classes and provides opportunities for student
 -led combos to form independently. The Advanced Jazz Band is among the nati
 on’s top high school jazz ensembles. 2022-2023 has proven to be another exc
 eptional year.</p><p>North jazz bands have participated in the Bloomington 
 Jazz Fest\, Purdue Jazz Fest\, University of Louisville Jazz Fest\, and Bal
 l State Jazz Fest along with ISSMA District Jazz. Several band members were
  selected for the IJEA All-District Jazz Honor Band. Additionally\, student
 s were chosen for the IJEA All-State Jazz Ensemble. Visit <a href="http://b
 hsnbands.com/">bhsnbands.com</a> to learn more about all the band programs 
 led by Janis Stockhouse and Thomas Wilson.</p><p><strong>Event Location</st
 rong><br>Bloomington High School North</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230316T141503Z
LOCATION:Bloomington High School North\, 3901 N Kinser Pike\, Bloomington\,
  IN 47404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:10th Annual Spring Swing Dance @ BHSN
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
