 🧼 Event Notes:</h4><ul><li><p>🧃 No food or drink vendors on site — plan a
 head!</p></li><li><p>🎶 Amplified music permitted from 6:30 – 9:00 PM</p></
 li><li><p>🗑 Trash cleanup handled by event organizers</p></li><li><p>🦺 Se
 curity managed by IU Police Department</p></li><li><p>🌧 In case of severe 
 weather\, the event will be canceled</p></li></ul><hr /><h4>🧭 Brought to Y
 ou By:</h4><p><strong>HoopBus Inc.</strong> – A 501(c)(3) nonprofit connect
 ing communities through basketball<br><strong>Indiana University Athletics<
