DESCRIPTION:We are gearing up for summer already and are pleased to announc
 e that the 2023 Get Outdoors Day event is being hosted by Hoosier National 
 Forest\, City of Bloomington Parks &amp\; Recreation and Indiana University
  Outdoor Adventures.  The 2023 event will be held outside on Saturday\, Jun
 e 10\, 2023 from 10 am to 1 pm at the Switchyard Park Pavilion Lawn in Bloo
 mington\, rain or shine!  This park is heavily used by local residents\, in
 cluding families.  For park details go to <a href="https://switchyardpark.c
 om/">https://switchyardpark.com/</a><br><br>We hope you are as excited as w
 e are to celebrate a day of healthy\, active\, outdoor recreation and fun. 
 Our goal is to have a variety of outdoor activities and destinations featur
 ed to create awareness of the many opportunities in south-central Indiana. 
  Hands-on\, interactive activities are a must.
