UID:e2006418706819661@facebook.com
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/2006418706819661/
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20260306T125958Z
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to WOE’s 2nd Indianapolis event —prepare yourself for a
 n experience like no other!\n \n🗓️ Saturday & Sunday\, November 7th & 8th\
 n📍 Indiana State Fairgrounds & Event Center\n🦇 Ag/Hort Building\n🎟️ VIP 
 10am-7pm\n🎟️ General Admission 11am-7pm\nChildren 12 and under are free!\n
  \n👁🎪Welcome to the World Oddities Expo- a traveling celebration of all t
 hings weird\, intriguing\, and magically macabre! We’re combining our love 
 of art\, history\, science and entertainment wrapped into one incredible ev
 ent! Shop till you drop from dozens of eclectic vendors and small businesse
 s. Grab a ticket to the Deformed Exhibit to indulge in rare\, preserved spe
 cimens that defy the laws of nature! Take a workshop in WOE labs and try yo
 ur hand at taxidermy\, rat skeleton articulation\, or create a miniature di
 orama terrarium and more! Visit our Main Stage for amazing live performance
 s throughout the day\, as well as surprise guest speakers for free seminars
 ! Whether you’re into oddities\, art\, fashion\, science\, or the culture- 
 this is your space to celebrate what makes you unique! \n\n💀👻DEFORMED EXH
 IBIT\nVisit our touring\, one-of-a-kind Deformed Exhibit featuring real\, r
 are specimens with medical anomalies! Snag a combo general admission ticket
  or a combo VIP ticket for those who want early access to shop before the c
 rowds.\n\n🦋🔬WOE LABS\nReady to kickstart your new favorite hobby but aren
 ’t quite sure how to start? Take a class at WOE Labs and enter a world wher
 e learning and creativity collide! Our knowledgeable and experienced instru
 ctors are there to guide you step by step. Don’t stress- all experience lev
 els are welcomed! Classes vary from city to city.\n\n✨️🎭 LIVE ENTERTAINMEN
 T \nWe curate only the best and most talented performers to take the WOE st
 age! You’ll find everything from contortion\, odes to sideshow\, clowns\, a
 s well as a few things you’ve never seen before! Don't miss these jaw dropp
 ing performances at the WOE Main Stage throughout the day!\n\n✍️🩸 ODDITY I
 NK PARLOUR- Only in select cities* Grab some new ink at the Oddity Ink Parl
 our and get a tattoo on site! Sponsored by Villain Arts and only in select 
 cities- we’re bringing you talented artists from all over the country. Grab
  those VIP tickets so you can be first in line for an appointment! \nThis i
 sn’t just an expo\; it’s an experience\, and you’re part of it. Get ready t
