 rday\, Feb. 14 from 11:30 a.m. to 6 p.m. Take a break while searching for e
 agles or stop by between scheduled programs. Complimentary hot tea\, hot co
 coa\, and snacks - also winter birding checklists and property maps.\n\n\n*
 ** 𝗙𝗥𝗜𝗗𝗔𝗬\, 𝗙𝗘𝗕𝗥𝗨𝗔𝗥𝗬 𝟭𝟯 ***\n\n𝟭𝟬:𝟬𝟬 𝗮.𝗺. 𝗕𝗼𝘁𝘁𝗼
