CREATED:20250125T183412Z
DESCRIPTION:Divorced Dad Support offers Peer Support Circles\, where you ca
 n connect with other divorced Dads in a safe and confidential space to shar
 e experiences\, gain insights\, and find strength in a community of underst
 anding.\n\nWe are committed to:\n\nOpen Dialogue: Share experiences and ask
  questions to gain valuable perspectives from fellow Dads who have walked a
  similar path.\n\nGuidance: When requested\, receive guidance on parenting 
 strategies and self-care during this challenging time.\n\nConfidentiality: 
 Safety is built when we can trust that what we share will remain with the p
 eople with whom we choose to share.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250125T183412Z
LOCATION:3820 E Moores Pike\, Bloomington\, IN 47401
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Divorced Dad Support - Peer Support Circle
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
