DESCRIPTION:The largest garage sale in Monroe County returns to 4015 Profil
 e Parkway. The warehouse is packed with treasures that are just waiting to 
 be claimed. From antiques to household items\, there is something for every
 one!\nCurrent MCHC members and Cook employees receive an early access day o
 n June 7! Join today at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://monroe
 history.org/join-and-give/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;u
 sg=AOvVaw1pxO1zCu8VbTC6Re4gWiHa" target="_blank">monroehistory.org/join-and
 -give/</a>.\n\nAll items are donated from the public and proceeds of the an
 nual Garage Sale support the preservation of the collections\, programs\, a
 nd exhibits of the Monroe County History Center.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230515T183046Z
LOCATION:4015 Profile Pkwy\, Bloomington\, IN 47404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:42nd Annual MCHC Garage Sale
